
                    // MoonScanner //
                      
             Simple tool to scann broken links


	~ What is MoonScanner?

	  MoonScanner can scan WACN(PPE) broken links and generate
	  result report with detailed info.

	~ How to use it?

 	  1. Install required packages:

	  	pip install -r requirements.txt
        
 	  2. Add urls to site.txt in such format (one url each line)

        https://azure.cn/documentation/articles/xxxxx
        http://wacn-ppe.chinacloudsites.cn/documentation/articles/xxxxx 

 	  3. Run the scanner
        
		python app.py
      
	  4. Review reports: good.md and bad.md for detailed info.
